data.description: UNICORN ALERT! 3948 SF, 4 BR OR 3 BR WITH 2 OFFICES, 3 full and 2 half baths. Spacious kitchen w upgraded Wi-Fi-enabled Jenn Air ovens & micro, prof. grade Kitchen Aid stove top. Family room w cozy FP. Downstairs primary suite w vaulted ceilings, custom walk-in closet, motorized black out shades, bath w dual vanities, separate shower & tub. 2 downstairs guest rooms w separate entrance installed. Upstairs game room, built-in desk, guest suite, media room. Great curb appeal w app-enabled jellyfish lighting. Smart home features, motorized screens, energy efficient tint on ext. windows. Outdoor kitchen, motorized screens, mosquito mist system. Pool w swim jets, waterfall. Scenic lakeside trails, resort pools, 2 golf courses, onsite restaurant & pickle ball. Future plans incl hotel & marina. Designated for Prestwick Stem Academy (grades K-5) & Strike Middle School (grades 6-8). 2 golf courses, resort style amenities lakeside trails. Minutes to The Star, PGA, Legacy West, Grandscape, etc.
